  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿嘿嘿，你选择和我以及 PeaceKeeper 合作了？好选择，干员！我们有个 BEAR 问题需要你帮忙解决。\n\n首先，你得知道，我们不能让你杀死任何 Rogue 或他们的头目，所以一定要小心避开他们。你的任务是在储备站和工业区击杀 BEAR 干员。同时，帮我们找一些西方武器——不要手枪，不要匕首，必须是高质量的西方主武器。记住，务必亲自找到这些武器！\n\n完成后记得向我报告。",
    "en": "Well well well, you chose to work with me and peacekeeper? Good choice operator! Me and him got something that you need to help us with, we got a bear problem.\n\nFirst of all you need to know that we can't let you kill any of the rogue USEC operators or their leaders, so be careful with them.\nYou need to take out BEARs at the military base and the industrial area. And while you are at it, go get us some western weapons, no pistols, no knives, proper western firearms, top quality. And make sure to find them yourself!\n\nReport back to me when you are done."
  },
